  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Something moved... but it’s not in the photo anymore.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the haunted halls of <strong>Mugen no Gakkou</strong>, a lonely Japanese school. As a rookie investigator for a clandestine paranormal research team, your only tools are your camera and your instincts. Document the anomalies. Survive the school. Don’t trust your eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by Japanese psychological horror and anomaly-spotting games, <i><strong>Paranormal Snap Shot</strong></i> is a tense, atmospheric experience where every detail matters. Rooms may twist when you look away. Ghostly silhouettes may flicker just behind your back. You won’t fight. You won’t run. You’ll only <i>snap... and pray it was enough.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/823af99de4065bf69932590342e65918.poster.avif?t=1744945226\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/823af99de4065bf69932590342e65918.webm?t=1744945226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/823af99de4065bf69932590342e65918.mp4?t=1744945226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anomaly Hunting Gameplay</strong> – Detect, document, and photograph anything out of place in looping, shifting environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Horror</strong> – Reality fractures the longer you stay. Expect classic Japanese horror vibes and subtle, creeping terror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Hard Mode</strong> – For players who want a greater challenge and even more disturbing encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secret Ending</strong> – A deeper layer of the mystery awaits, if you can find it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easter Eggs</strong> – Hidden nods, cryptic clues, and rewards for the curious.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Time</strong> – 1–2 hours per run, with extra replay value for full completionists.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/73d61d2ccd1ec6399110286fd5d158bb.poster.avif?t=1744945226\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/73d61d2ccd1ec6399110286fd5d158bb.webm?t=1744945226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/73d61d2ccd1ec6399110286fd5d158bb.mp4?t=1744945226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your camera ready. Not everything wants to be seen—<i>but they see you.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Something moved... but it’s not in the photo anymore.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the haunted halls of <strong>Mugen no Gakkou</strong>, a lonely Japanese school. As a rookie investigator for a clandestine paranormal research team, your only tools are your camera and your instincts. Document the anomalies. Survive the school. Don’t trust your eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by Japanese psychological horror and anomaly-spotting games, <i><strong>Paranormal Snap Shot</strong></i> is a tense, atmospheric experience where every detail matters. Rooms may twist when you look away. Ghostly silhouettes may flicker just behind your back. You won’t fight. You won’t run. You’ll only <i>snap... and pray it was enough.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/823af99de4065bf69932590342e65918.poster.avif?t=1744945226\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/823af99de4065bf69932590342e65918.webm?t=1744945226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/823af99de4065bf69932590342e65918.mp4?t=1744945226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anomaly Hunting Gameplay</strong> – Detect, document, and photograph anything out of place in looping, shifting environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Horror</strong> – Reality fractures the longer you stay. Expect classic Japanese horror vibes and subtle, creeping terror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Hard Mode</strong> – For players who want a greater challenge and even more disturbing encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secret Ending</strong> – A deeper layer of the mystery awaits, if you can find it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easter Eggs</strong> – Hidden nods, cryptic clues, and rewards for the curious.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Time</strong> – 1–2 hours per run, with extra replay value for full completionists.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/73d61d2ccd1ec6399110286fd5d158bb.poster.avif?t=1744945226\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/73d61d2ccd1ec6399110286fd5d158bb.webm?t=1744945226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337630/extras/73d61d2ccd1ec6399110286fd5d158bb.mp4?t=1744945226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your camera ready. Not everything wants to be seen—<i>but they see you.</i></p>",
